  - Beauty-Peace=Beauty=The Uncreate Source of Beauty
  - 505
By: St Augustine
---
The very order, disposition, beauty, change, and motion of the world and of all
visible things silently proclaim that it could only have been made by God, the
ineffably and invisibly great and the ineffably and invisibly beautiful.
